Use Cases:
----------

1. Ability to register a new user
	* create a new User & LoginDetail entry
	* should create a "User Registered event" (the event will be just saved to DB)
2. Ability to signin a new user
	* authenticate the User by validating UserName & Password
	* should create a "User Logged-in" event (the event will be just saved to DB)
3. Create a simple ML model to predict if the email is Spam (during registration)
	* ML model using Python